\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFireRock1009%2Fstatus%2F1152943059404873728%3Fs%3D20&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR1SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=61740fd5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFireRock1009%2Fstatus%2F1152943059404873728%3Fs%3D20&h=6a735ad8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/FireRock1009/status/1152943059404873728?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>高空拍攝 元朗站多名恐怖分子襲擊路人</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LifetimeUSCN/status/1152972148979523584?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLifetimeUSCN%2Fstatus%2F1152972148979523584%3Fs%3D20&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR1SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=305a5395\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLifetimeUSCN%2Fstatus%2F1152972148979523584%3Fs%3D20&h=eb84845b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LifetimeUSCN/status/1152972148979523584?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港人民質問到場黑警點解唔拉人同點解咁遲</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jeffielam/status/1152964501299322890?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjeffielam%2Fstatus%2F1152964501299322890%3Fs%3D20&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR1SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=b4a83176\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjeffielam%2Fstatus%2F1152964501299322890%3Fs%3D20&h=5916971c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/jeffielam/status/1152964501299322890?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>發動元朗恐怖襲擊前閱兵</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/zhangli63745952/status/1153022908417171460?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fzhangli63745952%2Fstatus%2F1153022908417171460%3Fs%3D20&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR1SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=ebf70a50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fzhangli63745952%2Fstatus%2F1153022908417171460%3Fs%3D20&h=72606e93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/zhangli63745952/status/1153022908417171460?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>恐怖分子 車內襲擊乘客</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RL220190531/status/1153024097879613440?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRL220190531%2Fstatus%2F1153024097879613440%3Fs%3D20&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR1SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=156acb4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRL220190531%2Fstatus%2F1153024097879613440%3Fs%3D20&h=e368e23b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/RL220190531/status/1153024097879613440?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>被襲擊既香港人民自衛</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/remonwangxt/status/1153149344058695680?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fremonwangxt%2Fstatus%2F1153149344058695680%3Fs%3D20&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR1SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=2e0c7819\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fremonwangxt%2Fstatus%2F1153149344058695680%3Fs%3D20&h=14eb57be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/remonwangxt/status/1153149344058695680?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n我地係時候要組織起嚟<br />\n守衛香港 保護香港人<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以武制暴</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>香港防衛隊由保安公司做起<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1344373\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1344373</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">五大訴求，勿忘初衷\n遍地開花，不撤不散\n打倒軍權，反對國家恐怖主義\n光復香港，時代革命\n\n\n\n一、徹底撤回逃犯條例的修訂，以至法理上終止條例程序\n二、收回612暴動定性\n三、撤銷對之前及今後所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、成立獨立調查委員會，徹底追究警察濫權\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行真正的雙普選</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n定性721黑警上環血腥鎮壓，元朗黑社會恐怖襲擊，警黑合作散播國家恐怖主義:<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警察戰線:</span></strong><br />\n警察冇預警下開槍射36發橡膠彈，有人爆頭，警察已無視通例，已失去合法性<br />\n警察放任黑社會打市民，完全冇制止，並假指無發現武器收隊，傳媒發現雙方實有公開溝通<br />\n警察公然無視電話求助，元朗警署落閘，違反警隊職責<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑社會戰線:</span><br />\n拉攏任何政治冷感市民，有錢人，元朗問題非個別事件，收錢恐襲任何區都會發生，任何人都有機會中招<br />\n俾藍絲睇到佢地支持何君堯即係支持黑社會打人斬人，令藍絲同何君堯反面<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國際戰線:</span><br />\n向外國抗議中國政府散播國家恐怖主義<br />\n向外媒及各國投訴香港警察包庇黑社會合作各自無差別打人，違反通例無預警開槍，已失去合法性<br />\n港鐵作為國際地鐵聯盟之一公然妄顧市民安危強逼市民離開車廂被打<br />\n黑社會涉嫌在元朗發動恐襲襲擊，主腦直指中共政府<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自發治安戰線:</span><br />\n強烈建議各區組織民衛隊，取代黑警職責<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港鐵戰線:</span><br />\n全面係所有車站招貼: 元朗站逼市民落車被打，妄顧安危<br />\n一定要令每個站每個角落都見到<br />\n全面不合作運動，再加宣傳市民全面罷坐港鐵<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">其他紀律部隊戰線:</span><br />\n拉攏非警察的紀律部隊，要求表態，為違反紀律部隊職責的警察投訴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n唔好忘記同日上環 黑警企圖殺害香港人民<br />\n［整合] 7.21上環開槍清場 有片有圖！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1348209/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1348209/page/1</a></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"818acdc19cf0a584d56d5c6d0e0783e94e609881","tid":1348771,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:57:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>記得幫手Backup</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"713c13b187293f49727c58490769a036dc5ea9ec","tid":1348771,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:57:12.000Z","msg":"push <br />\n而家做好文宣，spread去外國媒體。template睇下面<br />\n<br />\n【一月、二月】 David R. Stilwell<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.state.gov/biographies/david-r-stilwell/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Fbiographies%2Fdavid-r-stilwell%2F&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR1SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=a4dab835\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.state.gov/biographies/david-r-stilwell/</a><br />